<p><img class='alignnone' src='./images/ff5_part_1-1/05-shrine_of_the_wind_crystal-003.png' alt='' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 在此得知泰空王到了頂層去了，看來是要走一趟了</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' src='./images/ff5_part_1-1/05-shrine_of_the_wind_crystal-004.png' alt='' width='486' height='326' /><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'>-</span><br /> <span style='color: #ffffff;'> -</span><br /> 離開前可以到房間下面回復一下 ( 回復壺 )</p>
<p><img class='alignnone' src='./images/ff5_part_1-1/05-shrine_of_the_wind_crystal-005.png' alt='' width='486' height='326' /></p>
